@startuml Tasks_Code
!include <C4/C4_Component>

interface ICommandHandler {
   + handle(command)
}
interface IQueryHandler {
   + data handle(query)
}

class ApiController { 
    + IQueryHandler
    + ICommandHandler
    + IDataMapper
    - query(CollectTasks)
    - command(CompleteTask)
    + viewTasks()
    + completeTask(task)
}
interface IDataMapper {
    + Map(task)
}

ApiController --> ICommandHandler : send command
ApiController --> IQueryHandler : send query

ApiController --> IQueryHandler : send query
ApiController --> IDataMapper :  map data to correct format 

@enduml